The paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a topic commonly studied in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a novel GAN architecture, which involves learning a latent space and vector transformations, which are topics commonly studied in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
